      <h3>Learn More About Our Company</h3>
      <p>Planet Drilling Company has been a leader in the ground water industry since 2010, when it was first founded in Nepal. We are dedicated to providing our customers with quality well construction at a competitive price, and offering unparalleled customer service. Our company considers ourselves part of the community, and we value our commitment to providing a quality product that meets the needs of our customers.
      	<br/>
      	We are involved in drilling for the water well and rehabilitation of deep tube-well and shallow tube-well in soft sediments and hard rock terrains (e.g kathmandu valley, Terai Plain, Gompla in kathmandu, Bdal in Dadeldura and Changle in Gorkhara, and panckhal in Kavre district). We are registered with <b>GON<b/> department of industries and registered <b> VAT <b/> office.
      </p><br/>
